title: 227 - The Prodigal Son Returns; Gumpy’s Back
description: Today’s episode of The POD kicks off with a full barn as they all catch up from the weekend. With a rather candid start the boys then jump right into the Pod FOD which is a folder compiled of all things around the internet. Todays FOD includes Nick goin DAHN range a trip down 2000’s memory lane, a lot of AI updates, and much much more. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you Wednesday, Cheers.
